quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  44,1,Ha Mim
  44,2,Ndilumbira pali Buku limene limanena zoona
  44,3,Ife tidalivumbulutsa ilo mu usiku wodalitsika. Ndithudi Ife tili kupitirizabe kuchenjeza
  44,4,"Mu umenewu, ntchito iliyonse ili kuonetsedwa poyera"
  44,5,"Lamulo lochokera kwa Ife, ndithudi Ife timatumiza"
  44,6,"Chifundo chochokera kwa Ambuye wako, ndithudi Iye ndi wakumva ndi wodziwa"
  44,7,"Ambuye wakumwamba ndi dziko lapansi ndi zonse zimene zili pakati pawo, ngati inu nonse mutakhala ndi chikhulupiriro chenicheni"
  44,8,Kulibe Mulungu wina koma Iye yekha. Ndipo ndiye amene amapereka moyo ndi imfa. Ambuye wako ndi Ambuye wa makolo ako amene adanka kale
  44,9,"Iyayi! Iwo amakayika, amasewerera"
  44,10,Motero dikirani tsiku limene kumwamba kudzatsitsa utsi wooneka
  44,11,Umene udzazungulira anthu ndipo chimenechi ndi chilango chowawa
  44,12,"Iwo adzati, “Ambuye wathu! Tichotsereni chilango ichi chifukwa tsopano takhulupirira.”"
  44,13,Kodi iwo angachenjezedwe bwanji pamene kunadza kale Mtumwi amene anali kuwauza choonadi
  44,14,"Iwo adamutembenukira ndi kumati, “Munthu wophunzitsidwa ndi anthu ena, munthu wamisala.”"
  44,15,Ndithudi Ife tidzachotsa chilango pa kanthawi kochepa koma ndithudi inu mudzabwerera
  44,16,Patsiku limene Ife tidzakugwirani mwamphamvu. Ndithudi tidzawabwezera chilango choyenera
  44,17,"Ndipo, ndithudi, tidawayesa anthu a Farawo, iwo asanabadwe, ndipo kudadza kwa iwo Mtumwi wolemekezeka"
  44,18,Naati “Bweretsani kwa ine akapolo a Mulungu.” “Ndithudi ine ndine Mtumwi wokhulupirika kwa inu.”